rComments: He was a funny guy, not the best professor.  Material was pretty standard and you could blow off studying until the night before the exam.
He was funny and provided you with past tests.
Altaner tries very hard to keep the class interesting by showing a lot of videos and using the overhead. Lecture notes are online and old exams are available to study off of.

Pretty cool guy, tries to keep class entertaining by telling jokes and showing Far Side comics. Notes are posted on Blackboard, so it's easy to skip this class. Overall, relatively easy--not a bad class to take! Lots of videos on natural disasters :)
